        <li><strong>Committee Decisions:</strong> Loan officers don't have authority to approve</li>
        <li><strong>Generic Processes:</strong> Same timeline for all businesses, regardless of urgency</li>
        <li><strong>Bureaucracy:</strong> Multiple approval layers, internal reviews, compliance checks</li>
